 Mobility: The .FIVE-O Holster offers maximum mobility. Because the holster fits below the waist, it even provides for rapid withdrawal when seated.  The position of the weapon also allows for ease of movement when running, sitting, or engaged in defensive measures.  And because it accommodates most large and medium frame pistols, with a left or right-handed shooter, it eliminates the need for purchasing multiple holsters for different handguns.

title: For Sale:  M10
postcontent:
I have an M+M m10 ak I am thinking about selling. The ak has a few modifications done to it. It has a RS regulate 30mm optic mount with a primary arms red dot. The safety lever has a tab so you can manipulate it with your finger instead of taking your hand off the grip. The magazine release has a ambidextrous tab that can be pushed by your trigger finger to release the mag. The gas tube is kind of a hard to find part. It's a parabellum armorment ratchet charging system. It allows you to charge the ak from the left side of the gas tube like an mp5. It's a rare item you can look up the history of it or email me about it. It's a great system and hopefully they can produce them again in the future but for now there's just a few out there. The hammer and trigger have been worked on to give the gun a much smoother action. The handguard on the ak is one I actually fabricated and fitted with rails for accessories. It's completely sturdy, made from the same structural grade aluminum the m4 handguards are made from. It's lightweight and stays cool. If you don't like it I also have the stock hogue handguard that goes with. Also the stock gas tube comes with. There is 4 Croatian mags with the bolt hold open lips. 1 Korean mag, 1 tapco pmag, and 1 arsenal 10rnd mag. I have over 1200 put into this rifle so please serious offers only. May sell accessories if you want just a certain piece. I know it's a high price for an ak but it has a lot of high price accessories on it and and it's built up. It's also not a pos wasr. Great shooter one of a kind. Email for anymore information or more pictures, I can only get one to upload so it doesn't do justice.
